{"tid":2430522,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 14.5、iPadOS 14.5 Beta 3 推出　iPhone 12 支援 5G 雙卡雙待","createTime":"2021-03-03T04:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:13:01.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"08059f45927defd86a6111ee528788a90e5e427d","tid":2430522,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/03/03/ios-14-5-beta-3-now-available/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F03%2F03%2Fios-14-5-beta-3-now-available%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuiwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=c8573d8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/03/03/ios-14-5-beta-3-now-available/</a><br />\n<br />\nApple 今天為開發人員推送了 iOS 14.5 和 iPadOS 14.5 更新的第三個 Beta 測試版，距離上次 Beta 2 版本時隔兩週。iOS14.5 包含了許多新功能，包括使用 Apple Watch 解鎖 iPhone 的功能，本次更新的版本號為 18E5164h。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/iPhone12ProMaxPacificBlue-3-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FiPhone12ProMaxPacificBlue-3-2.png&h=837805f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本次更新對於 iPhone 12 用戶最大的影響就是支援 5G 版本的 Dual-SIM 模式，此前使用兩張 SIM 卡，即使你的 SIM 卡配備 5G 網絡，亦只能夠使用 4G 雙卡雙待，而在 <span class=\"red\">iOS 14.5 終於可以支援 5G 雙卡雙待。</span>"},{"pid":"3410c4b4de8c7c1598f03ee9b8238e4d76686ac4","tid":2430522,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/iPhone-12-5G-Dual-Carrier-Feature-orange.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FiPhone-12-5G-Dual-Carrier-Feature-orange.jpg&h=aa7090dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c1bd123d248409fb9b27c0c50f33b3e755c8a0e","tid":2430522,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":122,"score":-118,"c